{"tid":1823424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是你教我和平示威是沒有用的","createTime":"2020-01-13T16:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T16:28:29.000Z","uid":277298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ffc31cf1113e1274d7b1930545762a9b5a2973","tid":1823424,"uid":277298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"個陣反蒙面法，除左好多人講之外，<br />\n仲可以做到即日上街同開花，<br />\n令到d 阿叔阿嬸茶餘飯後都傾幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日又有單被自殺個案，仲要有埋片<br />\n但感覺好多人都只係IG FB 咁樣講兩句，就無回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選同Poly守衛戰後 <br />\n好似得返好零聲既手足裝修下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭活動日常化，可能只係對應到部分人<br />\n仲有一部分既人，佢地好難係平常日子參與到，<br />\n但又少左大型活動，所以佢地變相就無得再參與咁。<br />\n<br />\n的確好多手足話再勇武就等如送頭<br />\n抗爭既方式亦係時候轉變<br />\n黃色經濟圈亦見到果效<br />\n但少左街頭抗爭，真係令好多淺黃（例如我老母）無左回事。老母成六十幾歲，真係唔明和你shop 係乜，亦唔識得黃色經濟圈哩回事。係佢心目中，電視少播左新聞，即係場運動完左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係想屌想分化，我只係好想知道點樣可以keep 到大家心中團火。抗爭多元化會唔會係出路？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a85b1f5f4e3644590a4f246ff9b6d72d44775a0","tid":18234